    <entry>
      <title>Hi,markdown.</title>
      <link href="/2022/04/09/Hi-markdown/"/>
      <url>/2022/04/09/Hi-markdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><i class="fa-brands fa-markdown"></i>这篇开个新坑markdown的操作哈。<i class="fa-brands fa-markdown"></i></p><p>慢慢更新。如何更舒服的写md。</p><!-- toc --><ul><li><a href="#%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5icon">插入icon</a><ul><li><a href="#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEfont-awesome">配置font awesome</a><ul><li><a href="#%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDweb%E5%8C%85">下载web包</a></li><li><a href="#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEjs-css">配置js、css</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5icon">开始插入icon</a></li></ul></li><li><a href="#typorapicgo">Typora&amp;Picgo</a><ul><li><a href="#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEpicgo">配置picgo</a></li><li><a href="#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEtypora">配置typora</a></li></ul></li></ul><!-- tocstop --><h2><span id="插入icon">插入icon</span></h2><p>我使用的是这个<a href="https://fontawesome.com/">fontawesome</a> ，Font Awesome提供了很多icon的矢量图，只需要简单设置几步即可方便在markdown里使用icon。</p><p>效果如下哈。</p><p><a href="https://github.com/"><i class="fa-solid fa-code"></i></a>github</p><p><i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i>终端</p><p>十分舒服。</p><h3><span id="配置font-awesome">配置font awesome</span></h3><h4><span id="下载web包">下载web包</span></h4><p>在官网上下载最新版本的<a href="https://fontawesome.com/versions">web包</a></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/image-20220410002330259.png" alt="image-20220410002330259"></p><p>free的哈，足够啦。</p><h4><span id="配置js-css">配置js、css</span></h4><p>在hexo主题下的layout中找head.ejs这种全局的文件</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/image-20220410002645903.png" alt="image-20220410002645903"></p><p>在里面添加</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">defer</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/all.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">defer</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/v4-shims.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/all.css&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>到这里之后，就可以愉快插入啦</p><h3><span id="开始插入icon">开始插入icon</span></h3><p>在<a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons/">官网上</a>找到自己先要的icon。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/image-20220410003059745.png" alt="image-20220410003059745"></p><p>点击复制HTML代码。</p><p>在markdown下</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">只需这样就可以添加进去</span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa-brands fa-apple&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span>就可以添加图标</span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">&lt;i class=&quot;fa-brands fa-apple&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;</span>](<span class="link">&quot;zhujiyuan.xyz&quot;</span>)超链接</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2><span id="typoraamppicgo">Typora&amp;Picgo</span></h2><p>Typroa这个markdown编辑器，就不用多说了哈，优雅。</p><p>picgo是一个图床管理工具哈。</p><p>两者配合爽的一！</p><p><strong>把图片粘贴到Typroa时，会自动上传到图床上。</strong></p><h3><span id="配置picgo">配置picgo</span></h3><p>这里我使用的github的图床哈。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/image-20220410003924040.png" alt="image-20220410003924040"></p><p>自己建一个新仓库专门放图片等等，去GitHub里获取token（在github设置的开发者设置里）。填上即可</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/image-20220410004136550.png" alt="image-20220410004136550"></p><h3><span id="配置typora">配置typora</span></h3><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/zhu-jiyuan/picture_go/img/image-20220410004306971.png" alt="image-20220410004306971"></p><p>到这里就可以享受markdown图片插入啦。</p>]]></content>
      
      
